data.description:
Stunning 3 bed / 2.5 bath newer construction corner townhome on superior end lot in an A-RATED SCHOOL DISTRICT in the exclusive 24hr gated community of The Fields in Lake Worth. This beautiful residence features a spacious open floor plan with upgraded kitchen with a large center island with snack bar, premium wood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, stylish countertops and backsplash, tile flooring and recessed lighting throughout, separate laundry room with built-ins and sink perfect for functionality, the primary bedroom showcases extra space for reading nook, modern dual vanity and walk-in frameless glass shower. This home also features hurricane impact glass throughout, a 2-car garage and long paved driveway situated on superior corner lot with back open patio, privacy fence and open greenspace. 
Located in West Lake Worth, The Fields features countless resort-style amenities including Fitness Center, Community Room, Pool and Pool Area,Tot Lot, Mail Kiosk, Community Parks & Sidewalk, Barefoot Bar, Fire Pit, Grills,Half Basketball Court, Tennis Court, Spa and Cabana Restrooms - what's not to love! Residents of the fields enjoy being within close proximity to a variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment. Schedule a showing today!
